                    <div class="about-text">
                        <p class="reveal-text">
                            The Student Council is the cornerstone of student leadership, dedicated to fostering a dynamic, inclusive, and innovative campus environment. We serve as the official representatives of the student body, ensuring that student voices are heard and valued in decision-making processes. Acting as a bridge between students and the administration, we work to address concerns, implement ideas, and bring meaningful changes to campus life. 
                            Our mission is to empower students with leadership opportunities, encourage collaboration, and create a sense of belonging within the college. Through various initiatives, we promote academic excellence, cultural diversity, and personal growth. We strive to provide a platform where students can express their ideas, lead initiatives, and contribute to the development of the institution.
                        </p>
                    </div>
